<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Invitation Email</title>
</head>

<body>
    <div
        style="font-family: sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: auto; border: 1px solid #e1e4e8; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px;">
        <h2 style="color: #7c3aed;">🤝 In-Person Invite: {{meeting_title}}</h2>
        <p>Hi {{user_name}}, you've been invited to an onsite meeting at <strong>{{location}}</strong>.</p>

        <div style="background: #f3f4f6; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
            <p><strong>When:</strong> {{meeting_date}} at {{meeting_time}}</p>
        </div>

        <p>We use <strong>AI Meeting Intelligence</strong> to ensure no task is forgotten. Create your free account to
            view the agenda and follow-up tasks:</p>

        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="{{app_url}}/signup"
                style="background: #7c3aed; color: white; padding: 12px 25px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold;">Create
                Account</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>